Captain Marvel (Future Sticker)

The funny thing about this one is that…I don’t really like Captain Marvel. I still think her arc is rather weak all things considered (assuming she is indeed the strongest character in Avengers, the hero of the universe and etc.)

But do I like her design and outfit? Yeah, a lot btw. Which I think is the main reason why I’ve dedicated hours studying her clothing alone more than…well..reading her “comics”. Judge me. I don’t care.

summary: Dobson gets mad at YouTube for someone’s video having a different opinion than him, therefore “YOUTUBE IS FILLED WITH ALT...
body:
Dobson gets mad at YouTube for someone’s video having a different opinion than him, therefore “YOUTUBE IS FILLED WITH ALT RIGHTERS!”

Also apparently if you’re against SJWs, you’re an evil alt-righter, according to Dobson. All because one person said something about a video game Dobson likes.

I should not that Dobson didn’t even include the full comment he left on the video in his post. Here’s what he posted on the Facebook.

Because full context is “for Nazis” or something, I’m sure.

In fact, Dobson also reblogged a long tumblr chain about “Men only liked the Wonder Woman movie because they can OBJECTIFY HER!!!” by saying the only reason men liked the Ailita movie and not Captain Marvel is because OBJECTIFICATION!

Do you see what I mean when I saw Dobson’s reasoning about this kind of stuff makes him sound like the sexist one? Because this is a perfect example.

Oh, and in case anyone would like to watch the video that got Dobson so butthurt…

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yxc2Bq7UJj0

summary: Who is the true first Avenger?
body:
Who is the true first Avenger?

Captain America takes this title, typically, but what is the truth? Captain America was part of SHIELD first. However, Captain Marvel was the reason Fury started and named the project. Iron Man was the first Avenger who was actually recruited and joined the team. However, Thor is a god who has lived for thousands of years.
